    slug: 'jasper-ai-blog-tutorial',
    date: 'Apr 28, 2026',
    readTime: '10 min read'
  },
  {
    title: 'Best AI Tools for Small Business in 2026: What Actually Saves Time',
    excerpt: 'I tested 6 AI business tools for 3 weeks on real work. Here\'s which ones actually saved time and which were just expensive toys.',
